{"tid":1203193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父親節就到，父親當日幫我買橘子，我決定聽日報恩","createTime":"2019-06-11T11:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T12:10:17.000Z","uid":5939,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1a7046256cac36064be45386599498c96978b177","tid":1203193,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:48:48.000Z","msg":"我說道：「爸爸，你走吧。」他往車外看了看說：「我買幾個橘子去。你就在此地，不要走動。」我看那邊月台的柵欄外有幾個賣東西的等着顧客。走到那邊月台，須穿過鐵道，須跳下去又爬上去。"},{"pid":"27ed65725a5eedd180c7d9615bcccdd3730a5d25","tid":1203193,"uid":55810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697eb63fecafa92133343e9ef5dc95b6b2c64ffe","tid":1203193,"uid":5939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:50:34.000Z","msg":"佢禁肥都跳落路軌再爬番上來，我瘦佢成個碼，無野嘅"},{"pid":"2f32e92c93531e5b726207e1bbe9ba125a26184b","tid":1203193,"uid":39777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:51:12.000Z","msg":"CLS，好文章啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f66b4bb75dc199eef30292f32b91f0336b44d2","tid":1203193,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6223a96273533c60b5768771b9176743af26bf2","tid":1203193,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92eca7d73b314c431953998763533e1f7f271d36","tid":1203193,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:54:33.000Z","msg":"希望大家都報答下父親